tags.name: json-editor
tags.description:
`json-editor`
`simple JSON blob data binding to a text area`

Attributes:

  * `format-test` {`string`} - format test to update value so it's pretty printed

  * `current-data` - The current data object

  * `label` {`string`} - label for the text area

  * `error` {`boolean`} - State of being valid JSON object

  * `disabled` {`boolean`} - toggling disabled state of the editor

  * `max-rows` {`number`} - max rows in the textarea

  * `value` {`string`} - String based value of the editor, use this to set initial value

Properties:

  * `formatTest` {`string`} - format test to update value so it's pretty printed
